content: Your subscription to support and updates has expired

comment.text: This translation key is used to display a message indicating that a subscription has expired. It appears as a title in a UI component displaying payment settings, prompting users to renew their subscriptions or update their licenses.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Vaše předplatné podpory a aktualizací vypršelo' is a literal translation and sounds unnatural in Czech. 'Podpory a aktualizací' (support and updates) is a bit clunky. A more natural phrasing would be 'Vaše předplatné podpory a aktualizací skončilo' or 'Vaše předplatné pro podporu a aktualizace vypršelo'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Vaše předplatné pro podporu a aktualizace vypršelo

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Tuen ja päivitysten tilauksesi on vanhentunut' is a literal translation but could be more natural in Finnish. 'Subscription' implies an active ongoing service, and 'expired' often implies a grace period or final notice. A more natural phrasing would convey that the support and updates are no longer available.

While 'tilauksesi' (your order) isn't incorrect, it doesn't perfectly capture the concept of a subscription service in Finnish. It sounds slightly formal and transactional. 'Tuki ja päivitykset ovat päättyneet' conveys the idea that they have ended, which is more aligned with the English meaning of expiration.

The translation is technically correct but sounds unnatural in Japanese. "サブスクリプションの有効期限が切れています" is quite formal and literal. A more natural phrasing would be something like "サポートとアップデートの契約が期限切れです" or "サポートとアップデートの契約が失効しました"
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: サポートとアップデートの契約が期限切れです

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Twoja subskrypcja umożliwiająca uzyskanie wsparcia i aktualizacji wygasła' is a bit verbose. A more concise and natural translation would improve clarity.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Twoja subskrypcja wsparcia i aktualizacji wygasła

ai_spell_check_issues.description: While grammatically correct, the sentence structure could be improved for better flow.  Consider reordering phrases to sound more natural.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Wygasła twoja subskrypcja wsparcia i aktualizacji.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'සහාය සහ යාවත්කාල සඳහා වන ඔබගේ දායකත්‍වය කල් ඉකුත් වී ඇත' is a literal translation and can be improved for naturalness in Sinhala. While technically correct, it sounds somewhat formal and clunky. A more natural phrasing would convey the same meaning more smoothly.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ඔබේ සහාය හා යාවත්කාලන දායකත්වය අවසන් වී ඇත.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase 'to support and updates' is not accurately translated. While 'để hỗ trợ và cập nhật' is technically correct, it's a bit clunky. A more natural phrasing would convey the purpose of the subscription.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Gói dịch vụ đăng ký hỗ trợ và cập nhật của bạn đã hết hạn

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The use of 'của bạn' feels slightly redundant. Although not incorrect, it can be streamlined.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Gói dịch vụ đăng ký hỗ trợ và cập nhật đã hết hạn
